device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.M3D:3D Manufacturing Modeling System
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.MCD:Media Creation Device
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.PRINT:Hard Copy Print Server
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.CAPTURE:Image Capture
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.LOG:Procedure Logging
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.RT:Radiation Therapy Device
