device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OAM:Ophthalmic Axial Measurements
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OCT:Optical Coherence Tomography
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OPM:Ophthalmic Mapping
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OP:Ophthalmic Photography
device.dicomPrimaryDeviceType.OPR:Ophthalmic Refraction
